{"title":"Linux中man命令的使用","uid":"cff2c4bd24029dd1c648d80a4de194d4","slug":"技术笔记/Linux中man命令的使用","date":"2021-06-06T00:02:19.000Z","updated":"2021-08-21T14:44:52.063Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/技术笔记/Linux中man命令的使用.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1>man命令介绍</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Linux提供了丰富的帮助手册，当你需要查看某个命令的参数时不必到处上网查找，只要<code>man</code>一下即可。</li>\n<li>可以使用<code>man man</code>查看man的使用方法。</li>\n<li>man命令分为以下几个章节（按真实顺序排列）：\n<ol>\n<li>标准用户命令（Executable programs or shell commands）</li>\n<li>系统调用（System calls）functions provided by the kernel</li>\n<li>库调用（Library call）functions within program libraries</li>\n<li>特殊文件（设备文件）的访问入口（/dev）Special files (usually found in /dev)</li>\n<li>文件格式（配置文件的语法），指定程序的运行特性 File formats and conventions</li>\n<li>游戏（Games）</li>\n<li>杂项（Miscellaneous）including macro packages and conventions</li>\n<li>管理命令 System administration commands</li>\n<li>跟kernel有关的文件 Kernel routines</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>man命令的常用参数</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><code>man -f</code>:与<code>whatis</code>命令功能相同，可以简洁地显示命令的功能，以及它所属的章节。<br>\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210606220020.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li><code>man -k</code>:与<code>apropos</code>命令功能相同，可以在所有命令的manual页面中的Description部分中查找命令后接的关键词，然后对查找到关键词的页面简洁地返回一行描述，以及有该命令完整的名字和所在的页面。<br>\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210606220638.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>可以在查命令时，指定对应的章节，如：<code>man 3 sleep</code>只查第三节的sleep：<br>\n<img src=\"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210606220936.png\" alt=\"\">\n<ul>\n<li>如果不指定对应的章节如：<code>man sleep</code>，则默认查最小的章节，对sleep来说，就是Sleep（1）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>man的基本使用方法</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>翻页：\n<ul>\n<li>向后翻一屏：space(空格键)</li>\n<li>向前翻一屏：b</li>\n<li>向后翻一行：Enter(回车键) 或者j</li>\n<li>向前翻一行：k</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>查找：\n<ul>\n<li><code>/KEYWORD</code>: 向后查找</li>\n<li><code>?KEYWORD</code>:  向前查找</li>\n<li>在进入查找模式之后：\n<ul>\n<li>N：前一个</li>\n<li>n：下一个</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>退出：q</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"man命令介绍 Linux提供了丰富的帮助手册，当你需要查看某个命令的参数时不必到处上网查找，只要man一下即可。 可以使用man man查看man的使用方法。 man命令分为以下几个章节（按真实顺序排列）： 标准用户命令（Executable programs or shell...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":910,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"技术笔记","slug":"技术笔记","count":54,"path":"api/categories/技术笔记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">man命令介绍</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">man命令的常用参数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\"><span class=\"toc-text\">man的基本使用方法</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"ZestJourney","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://zjpicture.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/20210822091020.jpg","link":"/","description":"吾好梦中读书~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"QQ":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092319.jpg"},"WeiXin":{"icon":"/svg/weixin.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092515.png"},"Github":{"icon":"/svg/github.svg","link":"https://github.com/zestaken"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"我的书库","uid":"cbe4f79a31a9daca55fc549a629a4534","slug":"文/我的书库","date":"2021-06-06T10:19:25.000Z","updated":"2021-09-18T09:56:17.696Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/文/我的书库.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://zjpicture.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/20210918173443.png","text":" 吾好梦中读书~ 我的书库 点击我的书库链接或者图片进入书库。 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":43,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"文","slug":"文","count":3,"path":"api/categories/文.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"书籍","slug":"书籍","count":1,"path":"api/tags/书籍.json"}],"author":{"name":"ZestJourney","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://zjp